# WizTech Data Recovery - Complete Site Specification (Rev 2025 V1.1)

## Brand Identity
- Name: WizTech Data Recovery
- Primary Colors:
  - Color System:
  - Light Blue: #8ED8F8 (primary-300)
  - Dark Blue: #4B9CD3 (primary-600)
  - Full palette defined in tailwind.config.js
  - Color Usage:
    - Primary-300: Accents, highlights, secondary buttons
    - Primary-600: Main buttons, headers, important UI elements
    - Gradient combinations for hero sections and CTAs
    - Color Combinations:
      - Primary CTAs: primary-600 to primary-700 gradient
      - Secondary CTAs: primary-100 background, primary-600 text
      - Hover States: Brightness adjustment 105%
      - Active States: Brightness adjustment 95%
      - Disabled States: Opacity 50%
- Logo: Dual implementation
  - Primary: Image-based (/images/Final logo WIZTECH.png)
  - Fallback: Text-based with "WIZTECH!" in styled typography
    - Font weights: Bold for "WIZ", Medium for "TECH"
    - Exclamation mark in primary-300 color
    - Subtext "DATA RECOVERY" in gray-600
    - Spacing:
      - Letter spacing: tracking-tight for logo, tracking-widest for subtext
      - Vertical spacing: space-y-2 between elements
      - Logo height: h-36 (desktop), h-24 (mobile)
- Favicon: /images/WizTech Data Recovery Favicon 1.png
- Typography:
  - Headings: System font stack, semi-bold to bold weights
  - Body: System font stack, regular weight
  - Monospace: For technical details and code snippets
  - Font Sizes:
    - Hero: text-5xl (desktop), text-4xl (mobile)
    - Section Headers: text-3xl
    - Subsections: text-2xl
    - Card Titles: text-xl
    - Body Text: text-base
    - Small Text: text-sm
    - Micro Text: text-xs
  - Line Heights:
    - Headings: leading-tight
    - Body: leading-relaxed
    - Lists: leading-normal

## Core Architecture
- Framework: React + Vite
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Routing: React Router DOM
- Icons: Lucide React
- State Management: React Context API
- TypeScript for type safety
- Environment Variables:
  - VITE_APP_NAME
  - VITE_PROJECT_NAME
  - VITE_PUBLIC_URL
  - VITE_CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME
  - VITE_CLOUDINARY_UPLOAD_PRESET

