### UI Components

1. Service Cards
   - Accessibility:
     - ARIA roles and labels
     - Focus management
     - Keyboard navigation
     - Screen reader support
   - Performance:
     - Lazy loading
     - Image optimization
     - Animation throttling
     - DOM recycling
   - Icon integration
   - Description
   - Link to service page
   - Hover effects
   - Animations:
     - Scale on hover: 1.02
     - Shadow transition
     - Color shift
    - Card Structure:
      - Header:
        - Icon container
        - Title
        - Subtitle
      - Body:
        - Description
        - Feature list
        - Price range
      - Footer:
        - CTA button
        - Additional info
   - Layout:
     - Grid: 1 column mobile, 2 columns desktop
     - Aspect ratio: 3:4
     - Padding: 1.5rem
     - Border radius: 0.5rem
    - Responsive Behavior:
      - Stack on mobile
      - Grid on tablet/desktop
      - Flexible height
      - Maintain aspect ratio
    - Animation Details:
      - Hover scale: 1.02
      - Transition: 200ms ease-out
      - Shadow expansion
      - Color fade

### Assessment Flow Components

1. AssessmentForm
   - Error Recovery:
