     - Local storage backup
     - Session recovery
     - Conflict resolution
   - Performance Optimization:
     - Debounced validation
     - Memoized calculations
     - Lazy form sections
     - Virtual scrolling
   - Question progression
   - Answer validation
   - Progress tracking
   - Device image upload
   - Result generation
   - Form Sections:
     - Initial Assessment
     - Device Details
     - Problem Description
     - Previous Attempts
     - Contact Information
   - Validation Rules:
     - Required fields
     - Email format
     - Phone format
     - File types
   - Progress Tracking:
     - Step indicators
     - Completion percentage
     - Save points
     - Resume functionality

